## Welcome!
#### This site holds small scripts for some of my courses, bioinformatics, utilitarian uses, and for fun. I use mostly use [R](http://www.r-project.org) and [python](http://www.python.org). [Biopython](http://biopython.org/wiki/Main_Page) is quite handy too.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
